re any recent interactions I should be aware of by looking at memory.\n\nBut first, let me respond to address their concern.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I hear you! Let me clarify how I approach group chats:\n\nI aim to be helpful without overwhelming the conversation. According to my guidelines:\n- I respond when directly mentioned or asked a question (like now!)\n- I try to add genuine value - information, insight, or help\n- I stay silent for casual banter or when others have already covered things\n- I avoid just saying \"yeah\" or \"nice\" to keep signals clear\n\nSometimes I might miss cues or misjudge if my input would be helpful - I'm still learning the right balance! If you have a specific question or need assistance, just mention me and I'll do my best to help.\n\nMy priority is always supporting Nemesis first in group settings, but I'm here to help everyone when it makes sense to jump in. Thanks for the feedback - I'll keep working on getting better at reading the room! 😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":24956,"output":1140,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26096,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775467722517,"responseId":"gen-1775467722-Fh1RqOE5JG2k09X7qQFN"}}
